{"tid":282384,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"四眼Miss look陳霽平搵男友　有特殊要求","createTime":"2017-06-13T10:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T17:14:39.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60c9f511e3dcaf9d2bb63b455455379caeec3263","tid":282384,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"早前俾《壹》仔影到44歲嘅陳霽平Miss look教普通話，無論樣定身材，絕對冇走樣：「正常，又唔會話好多人追，正常囉。」<br />\n<br />\n之前仲有個話似Tom Cruise嘅西班牙男友，睇嚟唔多掂喎：「都會睇戲食飯，但就唔係一個serious嘅關係，因為佢始終住喺西班牙。」翻版Tom Cruise唔係幾啱佢心水，雖然已經44歲，但陳霽平又唔急，揀啱先最重要：「我見到身邊有朋友，佢哋拍拖或者結咗婚唔係真係好開心，所以如果有男友或老公的話，我一定要超越鍾意，唔會為結婚而結婚。」<br />\n<br />\n陳霽平話：「可能我自己要求比較高，我覺得真係要結婚嘅，就一定要真係啱，otherwise，我覺得唔需要結婚；我要求比較特殊，第一佢要做到我最好嘅朋友，要soulmate」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/iDoQooyHfgY/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FiDoQooyHfgY%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=b19cdab0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a436fea0894c5fb25905cbf77b1b1e8133e400bf","tid":282384,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:22:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98050a782f003b9a558d44d32b420f0ffe8df290","tid":282384,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>who？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"96fdd8c4187ab8349c68343f6fe4736d2ff0273a","tid":282384,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"四眼Miss look<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32c015996fddb52db141445b45e8115bdb5ef1a","tid":282384,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:26:29.000Z","msg":"四眼   miss look<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91311355fe7ccd15fb7b52629cadd83abc9fd19a","tid":282384,"uid":1254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc